snippet.title: Masters: Harukanaru Augusta 3-intro and gameplay-Sega Saturn
snippet.description: With the Masters about to start, started to play this little known but lovely Saturn Master Golf game. Yes I was rubbish , but having a drink with the Masters on TV :P
